Combining elements of Mr. Rogers’ gentle spirit and the unbound creativity of Jim Henson, Knight creates a completely original show that entertains and enlightens young children and adults alike. This is a cumulative song that's great for learning all about nature! That you ever did see.

and the hole was in the ground.
And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.

That you ever did see.

and the tree was in the hole,
and the hole was in the ground.
And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.

And on this branch.

The prettiest nest. 
That you ever did see.

and the branch was on the tree, 
and the tree was in the hole,
and the hole was in the ground.
And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.

And in this nest.
There was an egg.  
The prettiest egg. 
That you ever did see. 

Well, the egg was in the nest,
and the nest was on the branch, 
and the branch was on the tree, 
and the tree was in the hole,
and the hole was in the ground.
And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.

And in this egg.

That you ever did see.

Well, the bird was in the egg, 
and the egg was in the nest,
and the nest was on the branch, 
and the branch was on the tree, 
and the tree was in the hole,
and the hole was in the ground.
And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.

And the green grass grew all around, all around.
And the green grass grew all around.
